<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     8. PROCESS TIMELINE
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cd-process">
  <div class="cd-process__inner">
    <div class="cd-process__header">
      <h2>From Vision to Victory: Our Proven Process</h2>
      <p>Discover how we turn your ideas into reality with our streamlined, client-focused development process. From initial consultation to final deployment, our expert team ensures every step is meticulously planned and executed to deliver outstanding results.</p>
      <a href="/contact-us/" class="btn-orange">Get Started Today</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cd-process__timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="tl-label">Step 1</div>
        <div class="tl-line"></div>
        <div class="tl-icon"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <span class="tl-title">Have a Conversation</span>
          <p>We want to hear your ideas, learn your company's workflow, and offer our software expertise to find a solution to your frustrations while facilitating your growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="tl-label">Step 2</div>
        <div class="tl-line"></div>
        <div class="tl-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <span class="tl-title">Propose Solution</span>
          <p>Post conversation, we will send you a custom proposal with recommended technologies, a rough timeline, and a cost estimate to define the project specifications.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="tl-label">Step 3</div>
        <div class="tl-line"></div>
        <div class="tl-icon"><i class="fas fa-images"></i></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <span class="tl-title">Design</span>
          <p>Create low-fidelity (lo-fi) designs to outline basic structure and functionality, develop high-fidelity (hi-fi) designs for detailed visual representation, and build interactive prototypes for user testing and feedback.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="tl-label">Step 4</div>
        <div class="tl-line"></div>
        <div class="tl-icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <span class="tl-title">Develop, Test, and Deploy</span>
          <p>Utilizing agile methodologies, involving iterative development cycles, continuous integration and testing, regular feedback sessions, and seamless deployment practices to ensure the software is robust, scalable, and aligned with your expectations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="tl-label">Step 5</div>
        <div class="tl-line last"></div>
        <div class="tl-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <span class="tl-title">Post-Launch</span>
          <p>We stand by you and our work. After project completion, we warranty our work to make sure you are satisfied and will remain available for future maintenance &amp; optimizations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     9. FAQ
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cd-faq">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          What industries do you serve with your custom software development services?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a" style="display:block;">We serve a wide range of industries including healthcare, finance, retail, education, manufacturing, and more. Our custom solutions are designed to meet the specific needs of each sector.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          How do you handle security in custom software development?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Security is paramount in our development process. We implement stringent security measures, conduct thorough testing, and follow industry best practices to ensure your software is secure.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          What is the typical timeline for a custom software development project?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Timelines vary depending on the complexity and scope of the project. We follow an agile methodology, allowing for flexibility and timely delivery. A detailed timeline is provided during the project planning phase.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          Can you integrate new custom software with our existing systems?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. We specialize in API development and integration, ensuring your new custom software can seamlessly communicate with and enhance your existing systems.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
          <i class="fas fa-minus icon-open"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-plus icon-closed"></i>
          What kind of support do you offer after the software is launched?
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">We provide comprehensive post-launch support including maintenance, troubleshooting, updates, and enhancements to ensure your software remains effective and up-to-date.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     10. CONTACT + TESTIMONIALS
═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="cd-contact">
  <div class="cd-contact__inner">
    <div class="cd-contact__form">
      <h2>Let's Talk About Your Business Goals</h2>
      <form name="contact-custom-dev" method="post" action="/contact-us/">
        <div class="form-row">
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name" />
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required />
        </div>
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone" required />
        <input type="text" name="company" placeholder="Company" required />
        <input type="text" name="website" placeholder="Website" required />
        <textarea name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Describe your project"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-orange">Contact Us</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="cd-contact__testimonials">
      <p class="testimonial-label">What our customers say</p>
      <div class="testimonial-slider">
        <div class="testimonial-card active">
          <div class="t-quote"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
          <p>The Demski Group is great to work with! They inherited a mess with our platform and have been able to fix the bugs and make the platform more user friendly. They are also very professional and timely as well as a pleasure to work with! We have worked with Andrew Demski for all of our IT needs.</p>
          <div class="t-footer">
            <div class="t-author">
              <p class="t-name">Delaine Mast</p>
              <p class="t-role">CEO</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/our-clients/impact-team-tennis/" class="t-link">→ Read case study</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="t-quote"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
          <p>We spoke to a few different companies as we set out to find someone to create a website/database application to augment our desktop software. We chose The Demski Group in part because we found them very easy to talk to in our interview. That first impression stuck as we have a great relationship with them now.</p>
          <div class="t-footer">
            <div class="t-author">
              <p class="t-name">Mickey Rowe</p>
              <p class="t-role">Manager</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/our-clients/biopac/" class="t-link">→ Read case study</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="t-quote"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
          <p>Code quality was very good and done in a fast, efficient manner. We are pleased with the excellent job from The Demski Group. The team was able to provide high-quality services throughout the project. They produced the deliverables in a timely manner and within budget.</p>
          <div class="t-footer">
            <div class="t-author">
              <p class="t-name">Thariq Kara</p>
              <p class="t-role">CEO</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/our-clients/nu-borders/" class="t-link">→ Read case study</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="t-nav">
          <button class="t-prev">‹</button>
          <span class="t-count"><span id="tCurrent">1</span> / 3</span>
          <button class="t-next">›</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img class="testimonial-photo" src="https://demskigroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/two-young-intercultural-colleagues-discussing-code-2025-03-16-06-53-49-utc-1024x683.jpg" alt="colleagues discussing code" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ─── GLOBALS ─── */
  :root {
    --blue: #005cb9;
    --orange: #f09300;
    --navy: #001629;
    --ink: #282828;
    --muted: #f0f0f0;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

  .btn-orange {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--orange);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 14px 30px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-orange:hover { background: #d47f00; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* ─── 1. HERO ─── */
  .cd-hero {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 80px 40px 80px;
  }
  .cd-hero__inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 60px;
  }
  .cd-hero__text { flex: 1; }
  .cd-hero__text h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 50px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .cd-hero__text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 30px;
  }
  .cd-hero__image { flex: 1; max-width: 500px; }
  .cd-hero__image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  /* ─── 2. LOGOS ─── */
  .cd-logos {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 40px 40px;
  }
  .cd-logos__inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .cd-logos__inner p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cd-logos__inner img {
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* ─── 3. OUR SERVICES ─── */
  .cd-services {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 80px 40px;
  }
  .cd-services h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 50px;
  }
  .cd-services__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0 60px;
  }
  .service-hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .service-icon-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .service-icon-row i {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .service-title {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .service-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── 4. CASE STUDY ─── */
  .cd-casestudy {
    background: #f8f8f8;
    padding: 60px 40px;
  }
  .cd-casestudy__card {
